Items.MinutesNote: At this point the Speaker (Council Member Johnson) made the following annoucements:
Whereupon on motion of the Speaker (Council Member Johnson), the Majority Leader and Acting President Pro Tempore (Council Member Cumbo) recessed the Meeting subject to call.

There were 46 Council Members marked present at this Recessed Council Meeting of June 13, 2019 held on Tuesday, June 18, 2019.

(CM Lancman is considered Absent due to his absence from the Stated Meeting held on June 13, 2019 as well as the Recessed Meetings of June 18, 2019 and June 19, 2019, respectively; CMs Lander, Salamanca, Ulrich, and Vallone are considered Present but Not Voting for the purposes of this Recessed Meeting of June 13, 2019 held on June 18, 2019 due to their presence at the Stated Meeting held on June 13, 2019)

The Majority Leader and Acting President Pro Tempore (Council Member Cumbo) put the question whether the Council would agree with and adopt such reports, which were decided in the affirmative by the following vote:

46-0-0.
